<template>
    <!-- Header All Categories-->
    <HeaderAllCategories />
    <!--All Categories in page All Categories-->
    <AllCategoriesOn
        v-for="post in posts"
        :key="post.id"
        :id="post.id"
        :userId="post.userId"
        :title="post.title"
        :body="post.body"
    /><router-view />
    <FooTer />
</template>
<script>
import FooTer from "@/components/footer.vue";
import HeaderAllCategories from "@/components/HeaderAllCategories.vue";
import AllCategoriesOn from "@/components/AllCategoriesOn.vue";
import jsonpost from "../json/post.json";
export default {
    components: {
        HeaderAllCategories,
        AllCategoriesOn,
        FooTer,
        data: function () {
        return {
            posts: jsonpost,
        }
    },
};
</script>
